item.title: CVE-2018-18364|2024-08-05T11:08:21.470Z -- symantec%20corporation -- ghost%20solution%20suite%20%28gss%29
item.description: Symantec Ghost Solution Suite (GSS) versions prior to 3.3 RU1 may be susceptible to a DLL hijacking vulnerability, which is a type of issue whereby a potential attacker attempts to execute unexpected code on your machine. This occurs via placement of a potentially foreign file (DLL) that the attacker then attempts to run via a linked application.
